Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.90,0:00:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉近最討厭和最喜歡產生的距離
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.50,0:00:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是兩個人的推理和懸疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.50,0:00:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天來到了橫濱的中華街
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.20,0:00:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出現了跟小蘭有關的意外人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.20,0:00:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.80,0:00:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外表看似小孩 智慧卻過於常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.80,0:00:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字就叫做 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.00,0:01:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰向醍醐天皇提出了「意見封事十二箇條」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.50,0:01:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 三善清行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.20,0:01:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,描繪佛祖降臨淨土的畫叫什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.40,0:02:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「聖眾來迎圖」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.60,0:02:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 妳給我適可而止一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.50,0:02:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的頭都快要爆掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.20,0:02:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法啊 明天是日本史的考試嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.80,0:02:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,社團活動太忙了 最近都沒什麼時間唸書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.30,0:02:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以剛剛就叫妳待在家裡了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.10,0:02:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼 抽到中華街餐券的可是我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.80,0:02:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能讓我待在家裡呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.90,0:02:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那回去再看嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.30,0:02:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就來不及了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.80,0:02:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚還有很多想看的電視節目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.00,0:02:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過在車子裡看書的話會頭暈的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.60,0:02:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心 我耳朵裡的三半規管可是很強的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.60,0:02:40.40,Default4,,0000,0000,0000,,三半規管：專司身體平衡的構造
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.50,0:02:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.60,0:02:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下雨了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.90,0:02:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的 下得很大呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.00,0:02:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雨…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.40,0:02:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 那個人也是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.70,0:03:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個人也是站在雨中…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.70,0:03:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我忘了那是在哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.00,0:03:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陌生城市的街道裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.60,0:03:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有 為什麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.30,0:03:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每次想起這個男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.90,0:03:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個人的身影也會出現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.40,0:03:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.70,0:03:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一樣站在雨中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.10,0:03:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帶著悲傷溫柔表情的新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.00,0:03:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你也被淋濕了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.60,0:03:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼擺出那樣的表情呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.80,0:03:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新一 告訴我好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.80,0:03:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭姐姐 小蘭姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.50,0:03:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭姐姐妳怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.70,0:03:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,皺著眉頭看起來好可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.70,0:03:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 只是遇到了不會的題目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.60,0:04:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 向醍醐天皇提出了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.10,0:04:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 糟了 看樣子真的暈了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.60,0:04:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中華街 雨中的似曾相識（前篇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.80,0:04:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過還真是糟糕呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.30,0:04:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電影開拍前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.30,0:04:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女主角竟然因為車禍而骨折
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.90,0:04:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來還是不要拍這個電影比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.20,0:04:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像被詛咒了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.40,0:04:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 你有看過那麼有趣的故事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.10,0:04:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一旦拍出來了 一定很受歡迎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.60,0:04:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 川端先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.90,0:04:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易找來的女主角受了那樣的傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.30,0:04:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一般來說 已經沒辦法演了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.10,0:04:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.40,0:05:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是再那樣繼續的話 搞不好還會和前天一樣喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.70,0:05:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遇到大事故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.10,0:05:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了 骨折的那個女孩和我設想的女主角相去甚遠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.90,0:05:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的結果我倒是覺得很幸運
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.70,0:05:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,北浦老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.40,0:05:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 哪裡還能找到那樣的演員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.20,0:05:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身手俐落又年輕漂亮的女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.70,0:05:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 這是什麼意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.60,0:05:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼這個餐券不能用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.20,0:05:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.10,0:05:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是你看 這裡不是寫著的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.10,0:05:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個店的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.40,0:05:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 的確是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.10,0:05:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我們店的餐券
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.50,0:05:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.40,0:05:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那為什麼又說不能用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.40,0:05:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你給我好好說清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.60,0:05:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.30,0:05:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.20,0:05:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.60,0:05:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你姐姐叫什麼名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.30,0:05:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.30,0:05:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥你是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.20,0:06:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…我是誰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.10,0:06:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了小鬼 我的名字是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.30,0:06:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們這個店到底在搞什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.20,0:06:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道是會選擇客人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.80,0:06:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼可能呢 不是這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.60,0:06:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你少說廢話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.70,0:06:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這位客人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.50,0:06:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.90,0:06:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請到外面說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.90,0:06:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別以為能用蠻力把我們趕出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.50,0:06:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不說清楚我們是不會出去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.40,0:06:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇 你姐姐好厲害啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.80,0:06:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所…所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.20,0:06:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個餐券在週日和例假日不能使用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.40,0:06:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上面應該這樣寫著的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.60,0:06:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.80,0:06:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真的 上面有寫呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.30,0:06:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀 真是抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.80,0:07:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.80,0:07:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 沒什麼 只要能弄清楚就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.20,0:07:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過妳應該好好確認嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.40,0:07:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.40,0:07:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還不是老爸你說要快一點過來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.80,0:07:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.00,0:07:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 小姐 身手真不錯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.20,0:07:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以的話下次和我一起去看李小龍吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.40,0:07:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.00,0:07:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.50,0:07:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.00,0:07:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字是濱麥克 是本名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.00,0:07:28.60,Default4,,0000,0000,0000,,之後播出的偶像電視劇《私家偵探濱麥克》中的偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.60,0:07:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,濱麥克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.30,0:07:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 這個名字好像在哪裡聽過…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.10,0:07:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.20,0:07:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙就是濱麥克嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.00,0:07:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黃金町的橫濱劇場屋頂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.30,0:07:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.60,0:07:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個在電影院屋頂開偵探事務所的菜鳥偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.80,0:07:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.90,0:07:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了 小姐 感興趣的話打電話給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.10,0:07:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候都可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.80,0:08:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見 小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.80,0:08:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那個人是要幹什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.10,0:08:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.60,0:08:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,客人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.00,0:08:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問接下來 你們是否還打算用餐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.80,0:08:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那個 實際上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.30,0:08:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.60,0:08:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以的話就和我們一起用餐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.90,0:08:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然 是由我們請客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.70,0:08:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.90,0:08:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.50,0:08:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 電影女主角 我嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.60,0:08:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 是一個和妳很相似的角色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.60,0:08:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要妳願意的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.50,0:08:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.00,0:08:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了算了 到時候把台詞唸錯就太丟人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.30,0:08:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果妳能有我那樣被大家公認的口才
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.10,0:08:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就另當別論了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.30,0:08:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有那個口才的人是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.80,0:08:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.10,0:09:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.80,0:09:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果能在電影裡出名的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.30,0:09:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳也能成為明星喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.70,0:09:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還可以和很多藝人做朋友喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.50,0:09:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.20,0:09:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不止是藝人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.20,0:09:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,職業棒球選手啊 職業足球球員啊 F1賽車手啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.00,0:09:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拍電影的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.40,0:09:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還可以去美國 英國 法國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.60,0:09:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到全世界各個地方去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.30,0:09:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欸～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.90,0:09:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,試試吧 小蘭姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.00,0:09:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也是個挑戰啊 挑戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.60,0:09:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.60,0:09:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過如果想做的話 也要有心理準備喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.60,0:09:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 有些白癡製作人為了賺錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.00,0:09:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會違背劇本的原意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.60,0:09:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加一些無聊的愛情戲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.00,0:09:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛…愛情戲？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.20,0:09:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,北浦老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.60,0:09:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是在說我嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.30,0:09:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還…還是算了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.50,0:09:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是 太無聊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.20,0:09:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的…的確
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.40,0:09:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛情戲就怕成這個樣子 還是放棄好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.60,0:10:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一不小心的話還會喪命呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.30,0:10:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 不要嚇唬她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.90,0:10:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她剛還想答應呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.90,0:10:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有那個意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.70,0:10:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.50,0:10:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.00,0:10:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.20,0:10:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 沒有大礙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.70,0:10:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我用毛巾擦一下就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.10,0:10:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 服務員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.30,0:10:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩再拿一副碗筷好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.10,0:10:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的 我這就去拿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.40,0:10:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.20,0:10:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然有點發燒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.10,0:10:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.60,0:10:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係沒關係 只是有點鼻塞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.80,0:10:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果像上次一樣暈倒的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.50,0:10:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像上次一樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.80,0:10:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 沒有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.60,0:10:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐離妳那頑固的父親遠一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.20,0:10:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過來和我聊聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.50,0:10:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,點些妳喜歡的菜吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.20,0:10:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來幫妳點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.20,0:10:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.60,0:10:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.80,0:11:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.30,0:11:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 喂喂 我可沒點皮蛋和蟹肉炒蛋啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.00,0:11:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.10,0:11:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實我對蛋過敏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.90,0:11:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一看到有蛋的菜就覺得噁心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.40,0:11:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.70,0:11:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.40,0:11:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐 不要客氣 多吃點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.60,0:11:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那我就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.50,0:11:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要吃咖哩飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.40,0:11:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小朋友 這裡是中華料理店喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.80,0:11:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有咖哩飯喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.80,0:11:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我喜歡咖哩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.80,0:11:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要吃咖哩…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.60,0:11:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連咖哩都沒有 這裡太無聊了 快回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.30,0:11:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欸？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.10,0:11:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好不好 這樣比較好 小蘭姐姐？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.40,0:11:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.30,0:11:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 來 小籠包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.60,0:11:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南上次吃的時候說很好吃的對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.30,0:11:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.60,0:12:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 都不知道別人的心意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.20,0:12:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 醬油醬油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.20,0:12:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了 在叔叔前面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.80,0:12:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.80,0:12:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 可惡 又回到叔叔前面去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.40,0:12:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次一定要…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.40,0:12:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 又回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.20,0:12:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了柯南 想拿什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.20,0:12:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我想要醬油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.60,0:12:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.20,0:12:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.90,0:12:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 辣油在那個狐狸眼的大哥哥面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.70,0:12:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.90,0:12:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來 是要辣油吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.20,0:12:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是悲哀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.30,0:12:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒變小的時候是我照顧她的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.30,0:12:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 終於來了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.80,0:12:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個店裡的北京烤鴨最好吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.50,0:12:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.40,0:13:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有喜歡的女影星嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.00,0:13:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 有的 有兩個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.80,0:13:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個是藤峰有希子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.30,0:13:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實是我青梅竹馬的媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.50,0:13:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從小就很崇拜她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.20,0:13:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那另外一個呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.80,0:13:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有一個是美國的女影星 莎朗·溫亞德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.60,0:13:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過一年前去世了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.00,0:13:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 那個超級女影星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.40,0:13:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 見過她一次 很了不起的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.90,0:13:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳什麼時候見過這種人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.20,0:13:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在爸爸不知道的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.80,0:13:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過藤峰有希子和莎朗·溫亞德都很厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.40,0:13:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人都已經成為傳說了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.80,0:13:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她如果沒死的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.90,0:13:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定也能和她們一樣成為傳說呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.70,0:13:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是指
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.60,0:13:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.90,0:13:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.50,0:14:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被害者是川端四朗 四十六歲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.00,0:14:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電影製作人 死因是氰酸鉀引起的窒息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.20,0:14:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 氰酸鉀、砒霜、苛性鈉(氫氧化鈉)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.50,0:14:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近的罪犯都是從哪裡弄到這些毒藥的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.90,0:14:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死者死前吃了什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.00,0:14:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 北京烤鴨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.30,0:14:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死者用手拿著服務生包好的北京烤鴨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.10,0:14:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃下去之後就露出了痛苦的表情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.50,0:14:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 最後的晚餐是北京烤鴨啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.60,0:14:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還真奢侈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.60,0:14:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 北京烤鴨中檢查不出毒物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.30,0:14:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,服務生的身上也沒有氰酸鉀的反應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.90,0:14:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想必是死者在拿北京烤鴨之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.40,0:15:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手上就沾有毒物了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.00,0:15:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.20,0:15:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 那個持有毒物的兇手應該就在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.30,0:15:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和他一起用餐的你們這些人之中了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.30,0:15:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之 先說明一下你們和死者的關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.20,0:15:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們是製作電影的同事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.20,0:15:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女主角在開拍前受傷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.00,0:15:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家在討論這件事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.80,0:15:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是換主角還是放棄拍攝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.00,0:15:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後 川端就注意到了這個女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.20,0:15:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就叫她和父親過來一起吃飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.30,0:15:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那邊的小鬍子 我有在哪見過你嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.60,0:15:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是當然 因為我就是大名鼎鼎的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.50,0:15:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正在通緝的嫌疑犯嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.10,0:15:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.90,0:15:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.30,0:15:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是毛利小五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.30,0:15:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毛…毛利！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.10,0:16:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.50,0:16:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個名偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.70,0:16:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.10,0:16:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 那個沉醉的小五郎啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.20,0:16:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是沉睡啦 沉睡！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.40,0:16:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警部 這裡有毒物反應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.10,0:16:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.70,0:16:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他料理並沒有驗出毒物反應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.30,0:16:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有在死者所用的碗筷驗出氰酸鉀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.40,0:16:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,濕毛巾上是最多的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.50,0:16:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死者倒下時坐在他旁邊的是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.20,0:16:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我 我在他右邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.90,0:16:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那左邊呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.20,0:16:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.20,0:16:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.10,0:16:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在死掉的叔叔左邊吃小籠包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.10,0:16:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼這就很簡單了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.90,0:16:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把毒下在自己的濕毛巾裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.80,0:16:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再和死者的濕毛巾調換的犯人是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.70,0:16:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偵探先生 是你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.40,0:16:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.60,0:16:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種小孩又不會殺人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.70,0:17:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐在死者右邊的你調包也容易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.30,0:17:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且死者是慣用右手的人 毛巾一般也會放在右邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.20,0:17:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.80,0:17:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是早就料到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.50,0:17:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃小籠包之前會用濕毛巾擦手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.40,0:17:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說話啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.10,0:17:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這張臉好熟悉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.90,0:17:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別岔開話題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.00,0:17:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也好像在哪見過…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.40,0:17:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.70,0:17:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只在電視和報紙上見過你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.70,0:17:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,橫溝警部 過來一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.70,0:17:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.30,0:17:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,橫溝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.20,0:17:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對啦！你就是橫溝嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.70,0:17:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.70,0:17:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是因為辦事不力被剃光頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.40,0:17:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怕被我們認出來很丟人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.70,0:17:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就故意裝作不認識
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.00,0:17:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 是吧 是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.40,0:17:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我覺得你現在這個清爽的髮型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.80,0:17:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比原來那個亂七八糟的頭好看多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.70,0:17:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咳咳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.70,0:18:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是在靜岡縣警局的我哥哥橫溝參悟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.80,0:18:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是在神奈川警部的橫溝重悟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.10,0:18:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是他弟弟啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.50,0:18:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.60,0:18:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我哥待人隨和 他是很尊敬你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.70,0:18:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.60,0:18:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我壓根兒不相信你們這些偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.90,0:18:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個 警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.50,0:18:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.10,0:18:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死者牛仔褲上的這個痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.00,0:18:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.10,0:18:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是什麼湯汁的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.00,0:18:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那是川端先生的湯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.90,0:18:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我坐在他旁邊 不小心把它弄倒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.50,0:18:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 坐在他旁邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.20,0:18:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐在他旁邊的不是你和那個小鬼嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.50,0:18:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他倒下之前 川端先生自己要換座位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.10,0:18:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,插在了我和小蘭中間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.80,0:18:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那之後柯南又擠在了川端旁邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.50,0:18:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼在他換座位之前 在川端兩邊的是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.40,0:18:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐妳和…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.70,0:18:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.50,0:18:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過那只是他把偵探他們叫過來以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.00,0:19:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偶然坐在他旁邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.00,0:19:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在偵探他們過來之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.80,0:19:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,川端身邊的是我和他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.10,0:19:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過那個時候座位之間分得很開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.70,0:19:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一開始就在他的對面 應該跟我無關吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.90,0:19:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,調查一下就知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.20,0:19:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼也調查一下褲子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.20,0:19:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,川端換座位是在湯灑在褲子上以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.80,0:19:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他當時用濕毛巾擦了褲子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.00,0:19:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果調查一下褲子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.50,0:19:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就應該知道毒是什麼時候下的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.50,0:19:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 小五郎叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.00,0:19:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對…對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.60,0:19:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 褲子上沒有毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.20,0:19:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們好好調查了沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.50,0:19:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有服務生說之前湯被打翻的時候 筷子也一併掉在地上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.10,0:19:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以他給死者換了雙筷子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.00,0:19:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那雙筷子上也沒有發現有毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.00,0:19:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.40,0:20:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,調換有毒的濕毛巾是在換座位之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.20,0:20:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 那之後在死者右邊的你最可疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.60,0:20:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 哈哈哈哈 開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.30,0:20:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我今天是第一次來這家飯店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.10,0:20:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且還是初次見到川端先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.20,0:20:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我為什麼非殺他不可呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.70,0:20:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本來就很可疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.90,0:20:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你女兒第一次來這家飯店就被星探相中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.80,0:20:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪有那麼好的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.30,0:20:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.50,0:20:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的 我們真的只是偶然來這家飯店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.50,0:20:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.40,0:20:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雨…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.40,0:21:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然是在下雨天遇到了那個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.00,0:21:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他到底是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.40,0:21:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有和這個警官很像的另一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.30,0:21:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想不起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.80,0:21:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有三個人的臉一直在腦中閃過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.80,0:21:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,泛著笑意的嘴角
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.90,0:21:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,憤怒的雙眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.10,0:21:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.20,0:21:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.40,0:21:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.10,0:21:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我聽不到啊 新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.80,0:21:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭姐姐 小蘭姐姐 小蘭姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.20,0:21:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 臉色不太好喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.20,0:21:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 只是站得有點久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.10,0:21:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就過來坐一會兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.70,0:21:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想叔叔很快就會破案的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.20,0:21:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.00,0:22:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南可不要妨礙大家啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.80,0:22:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.20,0:22:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 小蘭神色看來不妙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.60,0:22:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不快點帶她去醫院的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.40,0:23:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.70,0:23:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去廁所的時候把毛巾拿過去下毒的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.50,0:23:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以就說不是我嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.70,0:23:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到都會覺得噁心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.50,0:24:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有沾上別的什麼東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.70,0:24:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 沒什麼特別的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.70,0:24:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.50,0:24:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有沾上別的什麼東西啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:12.80,0:24:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.30,0:24:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中華街 雨中的似曾相識（後篇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.50,0:24:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's Hint
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.50,0:24:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,濕毛巾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.10,0:24:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,私家偵探濱麥克啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:25.50,0:24:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那種程度的小案子就夠叔叔弄得灰頭土臉的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.38,0:00:18.76,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop my love for you{\fn4YEOVAL}A
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.93,0:00:28.53,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,在我們兩人所訴說的未來裡 就像有你在身邊的棲身地一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.06,0:00:32.16,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh baby I can't stop my love for you{\fn4YEOVAL}A
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.32,0:00:35.87,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,把我當作是你的全部喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.53,0:00:44.00,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,相信兩個人牽著的手 發誓我們一起走下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.12,0:00:50.85,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,“最討厭” 即使是謊言我也說不出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.88,0:00:57.90,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,“最喜歡” 如果是謊言我就不會說喲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.64,0:01:06.07,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,無法見面的時候 你就像無暇考慮其他東西一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.39,0:01:11.83,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你的心裡只有我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.53,0:01:15.91,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop my love for you{\fn4YEOVAL}A
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.07,0:01:25.38,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓兩個愛永不分離 請緊緊擁抱對方吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.29,0:01:32.60,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此不安的夜晚 還是會來臨的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.63,0:01:40.73,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,840)}那時候 要緊緊地擁抱我哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.30,0:22:28.44,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,每個清晨來臨的時候都會想起你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.68,0:22:34.45,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,只要在你身旁就覺得好幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.97,0:22:41.03,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,害怕因時間的流逝而哭泣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.31,0:22:46.24,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,在漸漸改變的人的心中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.95,0:22:59.84,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有期望也就不會失望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.67,0:23:06.60,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,然而不能沒有追求啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.88,0:23:13.98,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,無論前方的道路是何等艱辛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.85,0:23:21.07,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,在夢醒以後 你還是那麼遙遠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.34,0:23:26.62,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,只不過是自作多情的徒勞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.86,0:23:34.20,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,花雨中的道路還是沒有絲毫改變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.49,0:23:41.25,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,880)}真想挽著你的手漫步其中啊
